ope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !impo=
rtant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-botto=
m-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> did not work</a>, it ran out of m=
oney, and Helios &amp; Matheson filed for bankruptcy in 2020.=C2=A0</p><p s=
tyle=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Back in the day, I wrote admiringly about MoviePas=
s because it seemed so crazy, a leading example of how late-2010s consumer =
services were uneconomically subsidized by growth-hungry investors. (=E2=80=
=9CThe MoviePass Economy,=E2=80=9D <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbu=
