ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
we called it</a>.)=C2=A0But MoviePass was a symbol of wild incomprehensibil=
ity back in what was, in retrospect, a fairly comprehensible time. In 2021 =
every single thing that I write about makes less sense than MoviePass. =E2=
=80=9CBuy unlimited $10 movie tickets and give them to people for a $10 mon=
