><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Another theory you could have about ESG is th=
at it is a good=C2=A0<em>marketing=C2=A0</em>strategy; it maximizes the abi=
lity of institutional asset managers to gather assets. Coolly self-interest=
ed asset managers say to themselves =E2=80=9Cif we tell people that we are =
reducing carbon emissions and racial inequalities, they will give us their =
money to manage.=E2=80=9D There is some obvious truth to this one, and you =
don=E2=80=99t have to be cynical about it; big asset managers do say that t=
